com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registrars.repository

Class LazyRepositoryInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registrars.repository.LazyRepositoryInformation

  • public class LazyRepositoryInformation
extends Object
    Potentially creates a lazy proxy to wrap around RepositoryInvoker and Repository to delay the actual instantiation of these classes. This only happens when across.development.active is true.
    Since:
    4.1.0
    Author:
    Marc Vanbrabant
